item.dc:creator: @Xion Xion
item.description:
@Xion wrote:

[quote=“ThAt0n36Uy, post:17, topic:216772”][quote author=Xion link=topic=284947.msg2329573#msg2329573 date=1215829301]

According to him, it helps him deal with his anger problems but I think it makes them worse. I don’t understand how your personality can be improved by screaming at people over the internet, but maybe it’s just him

ThAt0n36Uy, I must say you don’t act upon your beliefs. You say you are christian and all that, yet you tell people to go die. Now I’m not a christian, but I do know that ‘god’ doesn’t like people who tell others to die.

I am a Christian, and I must say that he does not like those who tell others to go suck a cock, or say fuck you… If you are as big and bad as you act you would at least have a larger vocabulary than 4 words… (Fuck, Cock, Suck, and Die)… You seem to have very large anger problems… But telling people to go die in a hold does not make it any better. This just shows how self conscious you really are. So far every post of yours that I have read has been meaningless and lacks any common sense.

I have more respect for a Muslim who bombs the world trade center, because at least he actually follows what he says he believes, and acts upon it. I also have more respect for the Atheists who call me an idiot due to what I believe. They too are acting upon what they claim to believe. (Do not take this out of context. I did not say that I agree with the Muslim religion or with Atheism. I am just stating that at least they are more respectful to me due to the fact they follow what they say. As far as I am concerned you are the largest Hypocrite I have encountered yet.)

[/quote]

You continue to try and make me look like an ignorant fool. And it’s not working. You sit there and say my posts are meaningless. All you’ve posted is personal opinion shite. No one cares about your opinion. I’m self conscious? What in the HELL does that have to do with anything? Once again you say my posts lack common sense. I really don’t see that at all. I see it the other way around. I took a short amount of time to look over your posts too. It seems you have contradicted yourself multiple times. Usually lacking any form of real sentences. You may think you have me figured out. But you don’t, you know nothing about me. And trying to judge me my by posts isn’t accurate at all. I’m through arguing with you, it’s not getting anywhere. And nothing you have said has accomplished anything.[/quote]

If you hate me so much then just leave. The community could use one less person like you.
